            <a href="https://rosap.ntl.bts.gov/view/dot/3577" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Guide to Licensing Dedicated Short Range Communications for Road Side Units -</a>
          </strong>The goal of this document is to make licensing requirements transparent and best practices accessible to any organization, public or private, seeking to deploy “Connected Vehicle”
          Dedicated Short Range Communications Roadside Units and services that support V2X applications.
        </p>
